==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: magnifying glass
<hw>magnifying glass</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A single convex lens which
magnifies the apparent dimensions of objects seen through it, and is
used to produce an enlarged image.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hand glass.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Magniloquence</ent>⟦br⟧
